claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A table showing contraindications and precautions for individuals with previous severe allergic reactions (e.g., anaphylaxis) to different influenza vaccine types (Egg-based IIVs and LAIV4, cell culture–based ccIIV4, and recombinant RIV4) for the 2022–23 season. does not support the claim: the table addresses allergic reaction contraindications for various vaccine platforms and does not present any information on antigenic matching of Flublok with WHO- or FDA-selected influenza strains.
